title: Dakine Drafter 12L Bike Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Drafter 12L Bike Pack in Charcoal.
Drafter 12L Bike Pack Features:
- 100 oz. / 3L Shape-Loc hydration reservoir
- Air Mesh suspended back panel
- Full face or XC helmet carry
- Armor carry straps
- Fleece lined padded phon
